Liliana Laine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liliana_Laine 0 Liliana Laine was French film actress known for her roles in Italian cinema during the 1940s. She appeared in thirteen productions including the 1947 historical film Vanity. Liliana_Laine was French_film_actress known for her_roles in Italian_cinema during the_1940s .
